    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">The Revivex Suede, Nubuck and Fabric Boot Care Kit is all you need to safely clean and protect suede, nubuck, canvas and waterproof-breathable footwear like GORE-TEX® boots. The complete Deluxe Kit includes suede cleaner, a water repellent spray, a stiff brush to remove dirt, and an eraser block to remove scuffs. This cleaner creates minimal suds, while the water repellent keep your shoes protected from getting soaked and stained. If you already purchased our Deluxe Kit, refill it with the Revivex cleaner and water repellent. Or, if tools are all you need, order the Add-On Kit with only the boot brush and eraser. Extending the life of your favorite kicks is easier than ever with the Revivex Suede, Nubuck and Fabric Boot Care Kit.</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ff